    "en": {
      "title": "Former President Gotabhaya will come in early September",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will return to Sri Lanka in early September, according to government sources.",
        "He, who is staying in Thailand, said earlier that he will return to Sri Lanka tomorrow (24), but it is further reported that the trip will be delayed for about two weeks.",
        "Discussions are being held regarding the former president's security and other matters."
      ],
